platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: This app offers the flexibility you’ve always wished for when taking notes on longer documents. Quickly drag excerpts to a separate workspace, make comments, compare distant sections and more. You’ll forget how you ever read without it.

If your job or studies involve reading through longer works, LiquidText offers the kind of flexibility you’ve always wished for. Using gestures, you can quickly drag excerpts to a workspace on the side, make notes and comments or compress pages to compare distant sections. With support for popular file formats, sharing options and cloud services, it’s so intuitive to use that you’ll forget how you ever read without it.
這個 App 讓你在長篇文件上做筆記時具有更高的靈活性。快速將摘錄內容拖移至獨立的工作區、寫下註解、與其他地方的部分比較等等。你很快就會離不開這個 App 的閱讀方式。

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Easily make notes and comments on the documents you read.
